title: ‘Industry’ Season 2, Episodes 3 and 4 Recap
description:
Wosny Lambre and Jodi Walker recap Episodes 3 and 4 of ‘Industry’ Season 2. They discuss Yasmin’s character development, the fall of Eric, Harper’s ambition, and much more.

Hosts: Wosny Lambre and Jodi Walker
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
